reviewText: I had to send this back because I did not have a blue tooth player at the time but I have seen it on tv and as I always say, I love anything Chihuly
Beautiful DVD and beautiful pictures in the book. I love the DVD inside a small book format too. Dale Chihuly is amazing!!
This is one of the best DVD of this artist I have enjoyed his works are just Great. Wish I could see in person.
It was quite comprehensive and very entertaining. Full of great stories about the artist and his work. The scenes of the glass being created were fascinating.
I saw this DVD on pbs and had to have it!!  It took awhile to receive it bu, well worth it.
